---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About SNAV Marketing &#8212; Sydney Digital Marketing Agency"
  description="SNAV Marketing was founded by AV and Sanjit Babu to give Sydney small businesses access to expert digital marketing without the big-agency price tag. Meet the team."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">We Started SNAV Because Sydney's Small Businesses<br />Deserved Better.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">A digital marketing agency built by marketers who got tired of watching tradies, barbers and restaurant owners get ripped off by agencies that didn't deliver.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-lg story-grid">
      <div class="story-visual">
        <div class="story-card">
          <div class="story-stat"><span class="stat-num">2+</span><span class="stat-label">Years in the making</span></div>
          <div class="story-stat"><span class="stat-num">50+</span><span class="stat-label">SME clients served</span></div>
          <div class="story-stat"><span class="stat-num">$1M+</span><span class="stat-label">Ad spend managed</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="founding-badge">📍 Sydney, NSW</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="body-text">SNAV was born out of a shared frustration. AV and Sanjit had both worked inside large agencies &#8212; handling accounts ranging from national retailers to media companies. They were good at the work. But they kept seeing the same problem: small and medium businesses were paying a premium for strategy that was cookie-cutter, communication that was slow, and results that were hard to pin down.</p>
        <p class="body-text">They knew there was a better way. A model where a small business owner got the same quality of thinking as a big brand &#8212; just without the overhead, the account layers and the monthly retainer shock. So they built it.</p>
        <p class="body-text">SNAV (the name is a blend of their initials &#8212; <strong>S</strong>anjit and <strong>A</strong>V) launched in Sydney with a single mission: give local businesses an unfair advantage online. No fluff. No lock-in. Just real results that show up in your bank account.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section-pad" style="background: var(--bg-alt);">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <h2 class="h2 text-center">Meet the Founders</h2>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="avatar avatar-av">AV</div>
          <h3 class="team-name">AV</h3>
          <p class="team-role">Co-Founder & Director of Growth</p>
          <p class="team-bio">AV brings deep expertise in paid media &#8212; Google Ads, Meta, TikTok and programmatic. He's managed over $1 million in ad spend across industries from construction to hospitality, and specialises in building lead generation systems that scale. He's the numbers-obsessed one who doesn't sleep until the CPL drops.</p>
          <div class="team-tags">
            <span class="tag">Google Ads</span>
            <span class="tag">Meta Ads</span>
            <span class="tag">Lead Gen</span>
            <span class="tag">Analytics</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="avatar avatar-sb">SB</div>
          <h3 class="team-name">Sanjit Babu</h3>
          <p class="team-role">Co-Founder & Director of Digital</p>
          <p class="team-bio">Sanjit is the strategist &#8212; equal parts creative and technical. He leads website creation, SEO and social media strategy for SNAV clients. With a background spanning product marketing and web development, Sanjit builds online presences that not only look great but actually rank and convert.</p>
          <div class="team-tags">
            <span class="tag">SEO</span>
            <span class="tag">Web Dev</span>
            <span class="tag">Social</span>
            <span class="tag">Content</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Values -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-lg">
      <div class="mission-block">
        <p class="eyebrow-dark">Our Mission</p>
        <h2 class="mission-heading">"More customers. Less headache."</h2>
        <p class="mission-sub">That's it. Every strategy, every campaign, every report &#8212; it comes back to this. We're not here to impress you with jargon. We're here to put more money in your pocket.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🎯</span>
          <h3>Results First</h3>
          <p>We don't care how pretty the ad looks if it doesn't convert. Every decision flows from one question: will this bring in more customers?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🔍</span>
          <h3>Radical Transparency</h3>
          <p>You'll always know what we're doing and why. Monthly reports in plain English &#8212; no vanity metrics, just the numbers that matter to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🤝</span>
          <h3>True Partnership</h3>
          <p>We treat your business like our own. Your wins are our wins. We're not satisfied until the strategy is working &#8212; not just running.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🏡</span>
          <h3>Local Heart</h3>
          <p>We're Sydneysiders marketing to Sydneysiders. We know how locals think, search and spend &#8212; and we use that every day for our clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-pad cta-section">
    <div class="container-lg cta-inner">
      <h2 class="cta-heading">Ready to Work With a Team That Actually Cares?</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">Book a free 30-minute strategy call. We'll review your current online presence and tell you honestly what we'd do differently &#8212; no obligation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-white">Book a Free Strategy Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #152b47 100%); padding: calc(5rem + 80px) 0; text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #FF6B35; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .eyebrow-dark { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #FF6B35; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-align: center; }
  .hero-title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; color: white; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94afc7; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr; } }

  .story-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #152b47 100%); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .story-stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .stat-num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #FF6B35; line-height: 1; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #94afc7; }
  .founding-badge { background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); font-size: 1rem; }

  .h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .body-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .text-center { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .team-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .team-card { background: var(--surface-card); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.07); border: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
  .avatar { width: 5rem; height: 5rem; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 900; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .avatar-av { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F, #2a5298); color: white; }
  .avatar-sb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #e55a24); color: white; }
  .team-name { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .team-role { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #FF6B35; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .team-bio { font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .team-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .tag { background: var(--surface-2); color: var(--text-heading); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem; border-radius: 999px; }

  .mission-block { text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; }
  .mission-heading { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900; color: var(--text-heading); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .mission-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-body); }
  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  @media (min-width: 640px)  { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); } }
  .value-card { background: var(--bg-alt); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .value-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .value-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .value-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F 0%, #152b47 100%); text-align: center; }
  .cta-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #94afc7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .btn-white { display: inline-block; background: var(--surface-card); color: var(--text-heading); font-weight: 700; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9375rem; transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s; }
  .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.2); }
</style>

